		"description": "<p dir=\"ltr\">A blast of strong, sticky adhesive shoots from the palm of your outstretched hand, causing chaos on the battlefield.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The area of the spell becomes difficult terrain for the next 24 hours. In addition, creatures caught in the blast must make a Dexterity save. The creature then rolls on the appropriate table below to determine what happens to it.<strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Table: Failed Save</strong></p>\n<div dir=\"ltr\" align=\"left\">\n<table><colgroup><col width=\"45\"><col width=\"579\"></colgroup>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">1d8</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Effect</td>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">1</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Glue in eyes. Blinded until an action is spent to clear them.&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">2</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Mouth and nose covered with glue. Begins suffocating. Make a Strength save or Medicine check vs. your spell save DC as an action to open an airway.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">3</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Stuck fast to the ground and unable to move. Make a Strength save as an action to break free.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">4</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Covered in glue and Grappled. Make a Strength save as an action to escape.&nbsp;&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">5</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Gummed up with sticky goo. Encumbered until a minute is spent scraping the glue off.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">6</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Glue on entire head. Blinded, deafened, and suffocating. Each condition requires a separate Strength save or Medicine check vs. your spell save DC as an action to end.&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">7</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Badly disoriented. Confused for one minute; can attempt a Wisdom save at the end of each of its turns to recover.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">8</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Roll twice and apply both effects.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><strong>Table: Successful Save</strong></p>\n<div dir=\"ltr\" align=\"left\">\n<table style=\"width: 100%; height: 235.157px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 8.51064%;\" width=\"44\"><col style=\"width: 112.186%;\" width=\"580\"></colgroup>\n<thead>\n<tr style=\"height: 16.7969px;\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center; height: 16.7969px;\">1d8</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; height: 16.7969px;\">Effect</td>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 16.7969px;\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center; height: 16.7969px;\">1</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; height: 16.7969px;\">Snagged on a sticky patch. The creature is slowed until the end of next turn.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 33.5938px;\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center; height: 33.5938px;\">2</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; height: 33.5938px;\">Stuck, but easily freed. The creature&rsquo;s speed is reduced by half until end of next turn.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 33.5938px;\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center; height: 33.5938px;\">3</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; height: 33.5938px;\">Embarrassing glue placement. Disadvantage on Charisma checks for one hour or until a minute is spent scraping the glue off.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 33.5938px;\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center; height: 33.5938px;\">4</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; height: 33.5938px;\">Blasted with glue, but mostly unaffected; what is there is tactically useful. Has advantage on grapple checks for the next 10 minutes.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16.7969px;\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center; height: 16.7969px;\">5</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; height: 16.7969px;\">Eww, gross! The creature is rattled until the end of its next turn.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 33.5938px;\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center; height: 33.5938px;\">6</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; height: 33.5938px;\">Glues the creature to whatever it is holding. The creature cannot drop the item until a minute is spent cleaning the glue off.&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 33.5938px;\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center; height: 33.5938px;\">7</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; height: 33.5938px;\">Glues pockets and backpack shut. Accessing a stored item takes 1 minute until 10 minutes is spent clearing the glue off.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 16.7969px;\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center; height: 16.7969px;\">8</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; height: 16.7969px;\">Got lucky! No effect.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>",
